{"tid":1900974,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「一地兩檢」司法覆核上訴，排期下月11日審理 (2020.01.06)","createTime":"2020-02-27T14:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T14:27:03.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d4122950711605a46a1485ff2897e8eacee42640","tid":1900974,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:19:36.000Z","msg":"《廣深港高鐵（一地兩檢）條例》前年在立法會通過，並刊憲成香港法例，同時遭多人入稟高等法院申請司法覆核。高院其後頒判辭，裁定「一地兩檢」合憲，判申請人敗訴。「長洲覆核王」郭卓堅、社工呂智恆、前立法會議員梁國雄和香港民族陣線發言人梁頌恆早前申請上訴。根據司法機構網頁，法庭將於下月11日開庭審訊，預計需時兩天。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法官周家明早前裁定「一地兩檢」合憲，並在判辭指本港法院不應無視內地憲法，或將憲法視為無關重要，形容人大決定對香港有約束力。周官又形容，「一地兩檢」對香港整體利益帶來好處，亦符合《基本法》的立法原意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200106/s00001/1578287419221/%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%80%e5%9c%b0%e5%85%a9%e6%aa%a2%e3%80%8d%e5%8f%b8%e6%b3%95%e8%a6%86%e6%a0%b8%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4-%e6%8e%92%e6%9c%9f%e4%b8%8b%e6%9c%8811%e6%97%a5%e5%af%a9%e7%90%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200106%2Fs00001%2F1578287419221%2F%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%259c%25b0%25e5%2585%25a9%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%258f%25b8%25e6%25b3%2595%25e8%25a6%2586%25e6%25a0%25b8%25e4%25b8%258a%25e8%25a8%25b4-%25e6%258e%2592%25e6%259c%259f%25e4%25b8%258b%25e6%259c%258811%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%25af%25a9%25e7%2590%2586&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=d4e7f55d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200106%2Fs00001%2F1578287419221%2F%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%259c%25b0%25e5%2585%25a9%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%258f%25b8%25e6%25b3%2595%25e8%25a6%2586%25e6%25a0%25b8%25e4%25b8%258a%25e8%25a8%25b4-%25e6%258e%2592%25e6%259c%259f%25e4%25b8%258b%25e6%259c%258811%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%25af%25a9%25e7%2590%2586&h=d0616826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200106/s00001/1578287419221/%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%80%e5%9c%b0%e5%85%a9%e6%aa%a2%e3%80%8d%e5%8f%b8%e6%b3%95%e8%a6%86%e6%a0%b8%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4-%e6%8e%92%e6%9c%9f%e4%b8%8b%e6%9c%8811%e6%97%a5%e5%af%a9%e7%90%86</a>"},{"pid":"e5da8990b5254fca4d5cc18156fff9f5a195b836","tid":1900974,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:21:30.000Z","msg":"理論上2月11日開始審理一地兩檢上訴<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎後唔知會delay到幾時<br />\n<br />\n不過俾個消息和心理準備大家，<br />\n香港隨時在將來有機會無得再搭高鐵。"},{"pid":"9d0f5872cf723a8ba2fb437ac33e735b6ca9bdc0","tid":1900974,"uid":292700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"高鐵唔洗搭 係起出黎俾老解行過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319f34dfeb508766b93cd225d112988deb78835b","tid":1900974,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9d0f5872cf723a8ba2fb437ac33e735b6ca9bdc0","tid":1900974,"uid":292700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"高鐵唔洗搭 係起出黎俾老解行過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T14:27:03.000Z","msg":"老解唔駛搭鐵路<br />\n直接石崗軍營駛入黎市區就得"}]}